{
  "stem": "22944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell you if my saying that or from other spirit or something came over it, but he didn't put on the gas ring, right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, we did not know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shall we go hide behind the wardrobe?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It all looked so very, very stupid because it was a small room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shall we go behind the wardrobe, all of us, and hide there or whatever not?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it-- of course, dispose of all the bits of things we had around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the end, my feeling was, we surrender to the idea that we're going to be caught.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was like-- I do remember this so strongly that it was accepted that we are going to be caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How long had you been in hiding at this point?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose eight months or nine months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I didn't say-- tell you earlier that Pernik changed the lock of our door in the early stages because some people were suspicious.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had an incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A fellow upstairs or somebody downstairs tried to-- maybe the girlfriend-- maybe somebody who had a relation with the girl, we do not know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the lock has been changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a special key.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when he took the German around, for some reason, consciously or unconsciously, I could never test it, he gave him the old set of keys-- the previous lock we had on the door.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what's happened now is the German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went from flat to flat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now we can hear him going to the next door apartment to the man who knew about us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the singing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh, it was quite merry, quite loud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're talking and everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody gave a bit more to drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
